column1: # Tests system limits with high load
# Test Set 1: Baseline - Sequential Intra-Shard Writes (Cluster 1 only)
# Test Set 2: Read-Only Balance Queries (should be fast if optimized)
# Theoretical: 1000+ tx/s (if we implement read optimization)
# Test Set 3: Large Batch - 500 Intra-Shard Transactions
# Expected: ~5 tx/s sustained (100 seconds for 500 txns)
# With batching: Could be 500+ tx/s (1 second for 500 txns)
